ric-spec-297x277.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Surly-Updated-Big-Easy-Electric-spec-120x112.jpg 120w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Find out more, about the newly updated big Easy, or choose one of the many, many versatile and worthy steeds that Surly has to offer by hitting the link below. </p>\n\n\n\n<p><em><a href=\"https://surlybikes.com/\" target=\"_blank\">SurlyBikes.com</a></em></p>\n<p>The post <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/surly-big-easy-2-0-e-cargo-bike/\">Updated Surly Big Easy 2.0 eCargo Bike Gets More Comfortable &amp; Better at Hauling</a> appeared first on <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com\">Bikerumor</a>.</p>","author":"Ron Frazelle","siteTitle":"Bikerumor","siteHash":"49f427af0a926f4232eb837006841d7242e153e3afbb590f32e4b104ea3e2718","entryHash":"c6b0e802437a3714686549acb5c8dc75cd832cb6839c728574c085d6d5f1f27a","category":"Cycling"}